  Oracle Database Server Home.
  
  =item B<--tnsadmin-home>
  
  Oracle TNS Admin Home. Where to locate tnsnames.ora file (default: ${ORACLE_HOME}/network/admin)
  
  =item B<--tnsnames-sid>
  
  Oracle SID defined in tnsnames.ora.
  
